text: Johan Hove (born 7 September 2000) is a Norwegian footballer who plays for Strømsgodset and the Norway national under-17 football team. On 15 August 2018 Hove signed with Strømsgodset on a three years contract. ==References== Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Norwegian footballers Category:Eliteserien players Category:Sogndal Fotball players Category:Association football midfielders Category:People from Sogndal
